_text = "This memory doesn't exist. I never stayed behind. This last image was the last picture I took at this campsite before packing up my hammock and leaving. Sometimes I regret leaving. Could I have stayed another couple of days? Would I remember this place differently if I had stayed?\n\nI don’t remember how to get back here, but I hope one day I re-discover it again.I hope to create more memories here.\n\nI hope I get to sleep under the stars again in that very hammock.\n\nMy memory of this place ends here."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelRoom4, MemoryTunnelRoom4, false)
